ANTIBIOGRAM ANALYTICS SYSTEM
Professional Antimicrobial Susceptibility Analysis Software

Developed by: Abdallahjawadk
Website: https://github.com/abdallahjawadk/antibiogram-analytics

This software is designed for clinical microbiology laboratories to
generate and analyze antimicrobial susceptibility data according to
CLSI and EUCAST international standards.

DISCLAIMER: This software is intended for clinical and research purposes only.
The results generated should be interpreted by qualified healthcare professionals.
